  description: "abc update_abstractmethods code object attribute checks in abccode66 namespace — wave 237 theme: update_abstractmethods function code object attributes; update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_name=='update_abstractmethods' (module-level function; code object stores the function's simple name); update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_argcount==1 (takes only cls); NEW in extra66: first co_name and co_argcount checks for update_abstractmethods in the abccode66 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"
  kind: python_call_eq
  category: code
  id_prefix: abccode66a

  columns: [id, function, args, expected, description]
  rows:
    - [update_co_name,     update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_name.__eq__,     ["update_abstractmethods"], true, "update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_name == 'update_abstractmethods' — abc.update_abstractmethods is a module-level function; its code object's co_name is the function's simple name 'update_abstractmethods'; NEW in extra66: first co_name.__eq__('update_abstractmethods') check for update_abstractmethods in the abccode66 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"]
    - [update_co_argcount, update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_argcount.__eq__, [1],                       true, "update_abstractmethods.__code__.co_argcount == 1 — abc.update_abstractmethods takes only cls; co_argcount is 1; NEW in extra66: first co_argcount.__eq__(1) check for update_abstractmethods in the abccode66 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"]

