invariant abc_extra66.ABC_dict_mappingproxy:
  description: "abc.ABC.__dict__.__class__.__name__.__eq__('mappingproxy') returns True — Python class __dict__ is always a mappingproxy; ABC.__dict__.__class__.__name__ is 'mappingproxy'; NEW in extra66: first standalone __dict__.__class__.__name__ invariant for ABC in the abccode66 namespace; wave 237 first dict class name invariant for ABC; verified with Python 3.14.3"
  category: dict
